AND SOCIAL SHORT-TERM RENTALS ISSUES
***
1 This resolution reinstates the life and extends the reporting date of the Special Legislative
2 Commission to Review and Provide Recommendations for Policies That Deal With Numerous
3 Economic and Social Short-Term Rentals Issues from September 30, 2025, to September 30,
4 2026, and said commission would expire on January 10, 2027.
